[0m[49m[39m  289, 306[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  290, 307[0m:[39m[49m     // --- Utilization features ---
[0m[49m[39m  291, 308[0m:[39m[49m     // Healthcare utilization patterns signal disease burden.
